T13D4311-2:42a-19: mdze nad dang rlung dang khrag las byung ba'i dreg nad dang /

T13D4311-2:42a-21: klad pa 'khor ba 'di lta bu'i nang du 'gyur te /
T13D4311-2:42a-22: de lta bu la nad dpyad kyi cho ga bsil ba dang tsha ba dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-24: rtsub pa la sogs pa legs par byas te /
T13D4311-2:42a-25: gso sla ba 'dra ba las kyang ma phan par
T13D4311-2:42a-26: gyur na de lta bu'i khrag las nad du gyur
T13D4311-2:42a-28: de ni khrag lud pa yin pas rtsa gtar te khrag drangs na phan no //
T13D4311-2:42a-29: de la yang na gzhon te lo bcu drug ma tshang ba dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-30: rgas pa lo bdun cu lon pa la ni gtar ga gdab tu mi rung ngo //
T13D4311-2:42a-31: mi nyam chung ste khong na snum med pa dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-32: dugs sam lums byas te drags pa dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-33: rlung nad can la dugs dang lums byas pa lta bu dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-34: bud med sbrum ma dang bu byung ba dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-35: kha zas ma zhu ba lta bu dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-37: khrag nad du gyur te thur du 'khru ba dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-38: kha sna nas khrag 'ong ba lta bu dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-41: tshad pa drag pos btab btab pa dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-45: 'or nad lus thams cad skrangs pa dang /
T13D4311-2:42a-47: sngar skyug sman nam bkru sman nam /
T13D4311-2:42a-50: gtar ga btab pa 'di lta bu byas par gyur pa la gtar ga gdab tu mi rung ngo //
T13D4311-2:42a-51: gtar ga gdab pa'i thabs ni dbang bu'i phrag tu rtsa ba btsir ba drag tu mi rung ngo //
T13D4311-2:42a-52: dbang bu'i phrag tu rtsa btsir ba yon por gyur pa 'am /
T13D4311-2:42a-53: yon por gdab tu mi rung ngo //
T13D4311-2:42b-0: rtsa snang bar ma byung ba la gdab @42b tu mi rung ngo //
T13D4311-2:42b-1: nad dmigs dang sbyar na myung du gtar ga mi
T13D4311-2:42b-2: gdab tu mi rung ba la gtogs par ha cang
T13D4311-2:42b-3: grang lhags che ba'i tshe dang rlung che ba'i tshe
T13D4311-2:42b-4: dang / tsha ba'i dus dang nam rmugs pa dang /
T13D4311-2:42b-5: 'di rnams lta bu'i dus su gtar ga gdab tu mi rung ngo //
T13D4311-2:42b-6: klad pa dang mig na ba la ni dpral ba'i rtsa gtar na phan no //
T13D4311-2:42b-7: mig na ba la ni mig 'gram gyi rtsa dang /
T13D4311-2:42b-8: mig sgo sna drung gi mchan na yod pa'i rtsar
T13D4311-2:42b-9: thob shig / rna ba na na ni rna ba'i
T13D4311-2:42b-10: rgyab bshal ka'i mtshan bur thob shig / sna na
T13D4311-2:42b-11: na sna'i rtse mor thob shig / cham pa na
T13D4311-2:42b-12: na sna'i rtse mo dang dpral ba'i dbyes kyi rtsar
T13D4311-2:42b-13: thob shig / kha na na lce'i 'og gi rtsa
T13D4311-2:42b-14: dang / ma mchu'i nang gi rtsa dang /
T13D4311-2:42b-15: ya mgal ma mgal gyi rtsa dang /
T13D4311-2:42b-17: mgul pa yan chad na ste mkhur ba'i rtsa mdud yod pa dang /
T13D4311-2:42b-18: mgul pa dang rna ba dang mur 'gram dang klad
T13D4311-2:42b-19: pa man chad na ba la rtsa mdud dang nad
T13D4311-2:42b-21: smyo byed dang brjed byed kyi nad la brang dang mig 'gram dang dpral ba'i rtsa dang /
T13D4311-2:42b-22: 'gram pa'i mtshams su gtar ga thob shig / lus
T13D4311-2:42b-23: kun na ba la smin mtshams su byung ba'i rtsar
T13D4311-2:42b-24: thob shig /'bras dang rtsib logs su zug pa la
T13D4311-2:42b-25: rtsib logs dang mchan khung dang nu ma'i bar gyi
T13D4311-2:42b-26: rtsar gdab bo // rims nad zhag gsum pa la phrag pa'i mtshams su gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:42b-27: zhag bzhi pa'i rims nad la ltag pa'i 'og tu gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:42b-28: tshad pa bad kan kun 'khru na mjug to'i gong
T13D4311-2:42b-29: sor gnyis tsam du gtar ga thob shig / khu
T13D4311-2:42b-30: ba'i nad dam pho mtshan gyi nad la ni pho
T13D4311-2:42b-31: mtshan gyi rtsa la gtar ga gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:42b-32: mgul pa na ba 'am lba ba byung ba dang brlan na brla'i rtsar gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:42b-33: brla'i chu sul du rlung zhugs te 'gro mi shes
T13D4311-2:42b-34: nas rkang zug 'khums pa la pus mo'i lha nga
T13D4311-2:42b-35: na mar sor bzhi 'am lha nga nas gong du
T13D4311-2:42b-36: sor bzhi bcal te gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:42b-37: byin pa na ba la byin pa'i nyva 'bur 'bur po'i 'og sor gnyis su bcal te gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:42b-38: rkub tsos nas brla'i 'og thog thag byin ba'i bar
T13D4311-2:42b-39: du na na long bu'i nang rol na yar gong
T13D4311-2:42b-40: du sor bzhi bcal te gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:42b-41: pus mo'i lha nga'i 'khor skrang zhing na ba yang
T13D4311-2:42b-42: de bzhin du long bu'i gong sor bzhir thob shig
T13D4311-2:43a-1: pa snad de rdol ba dang /
T13D4311-2:43a-2: mthe bo'i tshigs kyi drung du sha rmen byung ba dang /
T13D4311-2:43a-3: rkang pa'i sha nang gi snam bu chad pa dang /
T13D4311-2:43a-4: 'di lta bu la rkang pa'i bol gyi tshigs nas gong du sor gnyis su bcal la gdab bo /
T13D4311-2:43a-5: rkang zug 'khums pa'i nad la yang de dang 'dra bar gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:43a-6: nad dmigs so sor ji skad bstan pa bzhin dun
T13D4311-2:43a-7: ba yang ma yin pa la nad dmigs ma mthun
T13D4311-2:43a-8: par snang na yang gnod par 'gyur ba'i nad zhog
T13D4311-2:43a-9: la / nad dmigs gar byung zhing gang du na
T13D4311-2:43a-10: ba'i rtsar thob shig / gtar ga gdab pa'i cho
T13D4311-2:43a-11: la / ga ni / sngar bas kha zas snum bag dang dugs kyi dpyad bya ste /
T13D4311-2:43a-12: lus 'jam zhing yang bar byas nas gtar ga'i yo byad dang /
T13D4311-2:43a-13: gtor ma gtang ba byas la bkra shis kyi cho
T13D4311-2:43a-14: ga byas nas kha zas snum bag dang khu sha
T13D4311-2:43a-15: la sogs pa zos la me 'de ba dang /
T13D4311-2:43a-16: nyi ma dron po la 'dug ste /
T13D4311-2:43a-17: lus dros par byas nas khri'u'i steng du tsog tsog por 'dug la /
T13D4311-2:43a-18: mgul pa yan chad kyi nang rtsar gdab na dar
T13D4311-2:43a-19: ram ras kyis bcings la skra yang gyen du brdzes
T13D4311-2:43a-20: te bcings la pus mo'i lha nga gnyis thog tu
T13D4311-2:43a-21: lag ngar gyi gru mos brten nas chang pa gnyis
T13D4311-2:43a-22: kyi bar nang du shing bal lta bu'i rlong bcug
T13D4311-2:43a-23: ste bcings la / mgul pa yang dar ram ras
T13D4311-2:43a-24: 'jam pos bcings la lag pa gnyis kyis rang gi
T13D4311-2:43a-25: gnya' ba nas 'khyud de btsir cig /'gram so yang
T13D4311-2:43a-26: sdoms la mkhur ba gnyis gang bar bus te lud
T13D4311-2:43a-27: pa ci lur tshir la mi gzhan gyis rgyab nas
T13D4311-2:43a-28: kyang tshir cig / mgul pa dar ram ras kyis
T13D4311-2:43a-29: bcings pa'i phrag tu rang gi mdzub mo g-yon pa
T13D4311-2:43a-30: ste bcings la / bcug ste / ma 'gags pa tsam du bya'o //
T13D4311-2:43a-31: khong pa'i nang gi rtsam gtogs par phyi rol gyi
T13D4311-2:43a-32: rtsa rnams bsdam zhing gdab pa'i cho ga ni de
T13D4311-2:43a-33: ltar bya'o // de ltar bsdams pas 'phral rtsa byung
T13D4311-2:43a-34: ste snang na sman pa'i lag pa g-yas pa'i mthe
T13D4311-2:43a-35: bos brtag cing mnams la sman pa'i lag pa g-yon
T13D4311-2:43a-36: pas 'phral gtsags sta re kha bzung la rtsa'i dbus
T13D4311-2:43a-37: ltar bya'o // su gtad de / sman pa'i lag
T13D4311-2:43a-38: pa g-yas pa'i gung mo'i bem tol ma yo ba
T13D4311-2:43a-39: ltar bya'o // su gtad de / dang / gtsags
T13D4311-2:43a-40: bu ma yo ma 'gul bar 'phral rtsa thob la
T13D4311-2:43a-41: khrag phyung shig / sna'i thor to dang mig sgo
T13D4311-2:43a-42: sna drung gi mtshan gyi rtsar gdab na /
T13D4311-2:43a-43: gtsags bu 'bras 'dra bas gdab cing khrag dbyung ngo //
T13D4311-2:43b-0: lce lkog gi rtsar @43b gdab na lce bteg ste bzlog la sos mnan te /
T13D4311-2:43b-1: lce'i 'og na yod pa'i rtsar thob shig / nu ma gnyis kyi bar dang /
T13D4311-2:43b-2: mgul pa yan chad na yod pa'i rtsar gdab na
T13D4311-2:43b-3: yang mchan khung ram mgul pa bsdams te rtsar thob
T13D4311-2:43b-4: shig / lto ba'i rtsar btab na lto ba thog
T13D4311-2:43b-5: tu mnyes la lto ba'i gong mchan khung du dar
T13D4311-2:43b-7: lag pa gnyis kyi chang par rdo ba chongs la
T13D4311-2:43b-8: lag pa bcangs nas gsum pa'i rtsar thob shig /
T13D4311-2:43b-9: lag ngar gyi gru mo nang gi rtsar gdab na
T13D4311-2:43b-11: lag ngar mi bskum par brkyang la /
T13D4311-2:43b-12: mthe bong chang par bcug la rtsar thob shig /
T13D4311-2:43b-13: gdab pa'i sa nas gong du sor bzhi bcal te
T13D4311-2:43b-14: dar ram ras kyis chings shig / rtsib logs gnyis
T13D4311-2:43b-15: kyi rtsar gdab na dpung pa gnyis thur du brkyang
T13D4311-2:43b-16: ste / khu tshur bcangs la rtsar thob shig /
T13D4311-2:43b-17: pho mtshan gyi rtsar gdab na pho mtshan gyen du
T13D4311-2:43b-18: theg la thob shig / byin pa'i rtsar gdab na
T13D4311-2:43b-19: brla man chad rkang pa'i bar du mnyes la sgab
T13D4311-2:43b-21: rkang pa'i bol gyi thog tu rkang pa ya gcig gis kyang mnan la /
T13D4311-2:43b-22: pus mo'i gong du dar ram ras kyis bcings la
T13D4311-2:43b-23: lag pas kyang mnan te rtsar thob shig / thabs
T13D4311-2:43b-24: 'di dang 'dra bar nad dmigs kyi gtar ga gdab
T13D4311-2:43b-25: pa'i dmigs ming gi bshad pa gzhan la yang nad
T13D4311-2:43b-26: gang du gtar ga gdab pa'i dmigs yod pa de
T13D4311-2:43b-27: dag tu bcing ba'i thabs de bzhin shes par gyis
T13D4311-2:43b-28: la thob shig / sha snag bu che ba'i thog
T13D4311-2:43b-29: tu gtar ga gdab pa'i ming gis ma bshad pa
T13D4311-2:43b-30: gzhan la yang gang dang gang du gtar ga gdab
T13D4311-2:43b-31: pa'i dmigs yod pa de dag tu bcing ba'i thabs
T13D4311-2:43b-32: de bzhin shes par gyis la thob shig / sha
T13D4311-2:43b-33: snag bu che ba'i thog tu gtar ga 'debs na
T13D4311-2:43b-34: / gtsags bu 'bras kyi srid kyi zabs tsam du
T13D4311-2:43b-35: thob shig /'phral rtsa ba rus pa'i thog lta bur
T13D4311-2:43b-36: gtsags bu sta re khas 'debs na nas kyi phyed
T13D4311-2:43b-37: / tsam gdab bo // rtsar legs par thebs nas
T13D4311-2:43b-38: khrag gzogs shig / ras sam dar gyis bcings la
T13D4311-2:43b-39: khrol phan chad ni khrag ma gzags shig / gtar
T13D4311-2:43b-40: ga gdab pa nyes na khrag zag pa'i yun yang
T13D4311-2:43b-41: thung khrag mang po mi 'byung ngo //
T13D4311-2:43b-42: de lta bu la rma khar til zhib tu btags pas gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:44a-1: ha cang gdab drags na khrag thor zhes 'byung ba dang /
T13D4311-2:44a-3: khrag gcad kyang dka' bar 'gyur la /
T13D4311-2:44a-6: yang na bsdams pa lhod dam /
T13D4311-2:44a-7: mtshon rtul lam zas skom 'grangs shing ngoms ches sam /
T13D4311-2:44a-9: bshang gci'i shugs 'ong bar gyur tam /
T13D4311-2:44a-10: dugs lta bu drags na yang khrag dbyung ngu mi rung ngo //
T13D4311-2:44a-11: khrag de ltar 'ong du mi rung na /
T13D4311-2:44a-18: khang pa'i ka gdung la chags pa'i dud pa dang /
T13D4311-2:44a-19: lce myang tsha 'di rnams btags te til mar dang
T13D4311-2:44a-20: sbyar la rma khar skus shig / khrag legs par
T13D4311-2:44a-21: byung na rma khar til mar dro 'jam tsam dang
T13D4311-2:44a-22: / lce myang tsha skus shig / gtar ga gdab
T13D4311-2:44a-23: pa la dang por nad khrag chu ser le brgan
T13D4311-2:44a-25: nad khrag legs par byung nas khrag rang 'chad do //
T13D4311-2:44a-26: yang na khrag bzang po byung na des chog gis
T13D4311-2:44a-27: bcings pa khrol cig / gal te 'bog ste brgyal
T13D4311-2:44a-28: na bcings pa khrol la bsil yab kyis g-yobs te
T13D4311-2:44a-29: brtas pa dang khrag slar yang phyung shig / yang
T13D4311-2:44a-30: 'bog par gyur na nyi ma gnyis gsum ngal sos
T13D4311-2:44a-31: la thob shig / de la rlung nad kyi khrag
T13D4311-2:44a-32: ni gnag la rtsa dmar ba dang /
T13D4311-2:44a-33: khrag mdog rtsub pa khrag dbyung ba'i shugs drag /
T13D4311-2:44a-34: mdog gsal la dbu pa can du 'dug go /
T13D4311-2:44a-35: mkhris pa'i nad khrag ni bsil zhing ser la rtsa
T13D4311-2:44a-36: gnag mnam la spyi bag can khrag ska ste myur
T13D4311-2:44a-37: du mi 'byung / khrag drod che ste tsha la kha dog tshon can du snang ngo //
T13D4311-2:44a-38: bad kan gyi khrag nad ni 'jam la cung zad rtsa dkar la drangs na nal nal byed /
T13D4311-2:44a-39: lag pas myangs na 'byil ba'i 'byar pag tu byed pa ska'o //
T13D4311-2:44a-42: bad kan gsum char 'dres pa'i nad khrag ni ngan zhing de gsum gyi tshul 'dres par yod la /
T13D4311-2:44a-43: khrag mdog gnag cing kun 'dres par 'dug pa'o //
T13D4311-2:44a-44: nad pa'i khrag ngan na nyams che yang rung khrag
T13D4311-2:44a-45: srang bzhi bcu rtsa bdun tsam las dbyung du mi
T13D4311-2:44a-46: rung ngo // khrag ha cang dbyung drags na 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
T13D4311-2:44a-47: de bas na khrag dbyung drags na rlung nad kyi dkyel mi bzad pa skye'o //
T13D4311-2:44a-48: de la ltag khrag dbyung drags pa las lus mar gyis byug cing mnyes te /
T13D4311-2:44b-0: @44b bcud dang 'o ma dang khrag bcud dang kha zas bsod pa bza'/
T13D4311-2:44b-1: rlung nad la phan pa'i sman gtang ngo //
T13D4311-2:44b-2: gtar ga btab ste khrag chod pa dang til mar gyi nang du ras 'jam po 'am /
T13D4311-2:44b-3: bal gyi ye'u smyugs la rma khar bskus la /
T13D4311-2:44b-6: dar gyis bcings pa dal gyis glod la chu bsil
T13D4311-2:44b-7: bas khrus shig / nad khrag tu gyur te khrag
T13D4311-2:44b-8: ngan na ni phye ma 'phred bskyar ro //
T13D4311-2:44b-9: yang na phyi de nyin skyor cig / nad pa
T13D4311-2:44b-10: sngar nyams brtas te snum bag gi cho ga byas
T13D4311-2:44b-11: pa zhig na ni nyams kyis thub pa yin te
T13D4311-2:44b-12: / cho ga byas nas zhag gnyis nas gtar ga
T13D4311-2:44b-13: thob shig / nad pa nyam chung na ni zla
T13D4311-2:44b-14: ba phyed tsam du snum bag gis brtas te /
T13D4311-2:44b-15: de nas gtar ga thob shig / gtar ga btab ste /
T13D4311-2:44b-16: nad khrag gi 'phro lus kyang cung zad the ge
T13D4311-2:44b-17: ba ltar byed na ni khrag gi 'phro lhag ma
T13D4311-2:44b-19: ha cang dbyung drags par mi bya'o //
T13D4311-2:44b-20: gal te rngabs rus nyi tsher gzhibs pa'i dmigs shig
T13D4311-2:44b-21: yod na ni rngabs rus thob shig / yang na
T13D4311-2:44b-23: nad khrag ngan pa 'byung zhing bstsal bar 'gyur ba'i
T13D4311-2:44b-24: sman thong shig sman gtang ba'i dmigs ni mkhris pa
T13D4311-2:44b-25: rgyas pa las khrag lud de na bar 'gyur ro
T13D4311-2:44b-26: // de lta bu la dmigs kyi bye brag tu bya ba ni /
T13D4311-2:44b-27: bkru sman dang skyug sman gyis bkrus la mkhris pa
T13D4311-2:44b-28: tsha ba'i nad la phan pa'i sman bsil bag thong
T13D4311-2:44b-29: shig / nad khrag ngan pa yin gyis kyang khrag
T13D4311-2:44b-30: rgyas pa tsam du ma gyur na nad khrag 'byang
T13D4311-2:44b-31: zhing bags kyis dbyung ba'i sman gtang ba'i thabs ni
T13D4311-2:44b-32: de ltar bya'o // gtar ga gdab pa zhig la
T13D4311-2:44b-33: khrag mi chod na gcod pa'i sman ni ro dra
T13D4311-2:44b-34: de ltar bya'o // seng phrom dang / gandha pri yang ku dang rma shing dang /
T13D4311-2:44b-38: sa nag po spyi ba dang /
T13D4311-2:44b-43: khre dang 'di rnams cha snyoms te zhib tu btags
T13D4311-2:44b-44: la rma khar thob shig / bsil ba'i sman shug
T13D4311-2:44b-45: pa la sogs pa btags te chu dang sbyar la
T13D4311-2:44b-46: blud do // yang na de ltar khrag mi chod pa dang /
T13D4311-2:44b-47: rtsa de gnyis kyi gong du gtar ga gdab bo //
T13D4311-2:44b-48: yang na thur ma bsregs pas rma khar sregs shig
T13D4311-2:44b-49: / gtar ga gdab pa'i bcing ba ma legs sam
T13D4311-2:44b-50: / dbang bu la gdab pa ma legs te /
T13D4311-2:44b-51: yo bas nad khrag ma phyin tam /
T13D4311-2:45a-0: @45a * // khrag mangs pa lta bur gyur pas rlung dang mkhris
T13D4311-2:45a-1: pa dang bad kan gyi nad rgyas pas nad khrag
T13D4311-2:45a-2: ngan par gyur pas rlung dang mkhris pa dang bad
T13D4311-2:45a-3: kan rang gi gnas su ma phebs ma lon gyi
T13D4311-2:45a-4: bar du kha zas phan zhing 'phrod pa dang /
T13D4311-2:45a-5: byed cing bskyod pa yang phan pa'i tshul du bya zhing bsten to //
T13D4311-2:45a-6: kha zas ni ha cang tsha ba dang bsil ba yang ma yin /
T13D4311-2:45a-7: yang la 'ju sla ba de lta bu'i zas skom bzang ste /
T13D4311-2:45a-8: de ltar gtar ga gdab pas drod kyang lhag par
T13D4311-2:45a-9: chung la rlung dang mkhris pa dang bad kan gsum
T13D4311-2:45a-10: rang gi gnas su babs pa na phan pa'i cho
T13D4311-2:45a-11: ga bya zhing de ltar bsrung dgos so //
T13D4311-2:45a-12: gtar ga legs pa ni bzhin mdog dang dbang po
T13D4311-2:45a-13: rnams dang zhing gsal ba dang mig la sogs pa

T13D4311-2:145b-36: lus kyi lhu tshigs yan lag rengs /
T13D4311-2:145b-37: khu tshur dang dbyig pas phog pa snyam byed do //
T13D4311-2:145b-38: rus pa la rlung nad zhugs na brla dang byin
T13D4311-2:145b-39: pa rje dar rab tu rkang zug phyogs su na
T13D4311-2:145b-41: nyams stobs rab tu zad par byed do //
T13D4311-2:145b-42: rkang la rlung nad zhugs na /
T13D4311-2:145b-45: khu ba la rlung nad zhugs na yang na khu ba myur du 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
T13D4311-2:145b-46: yang na khu ba 'byung du mi rung ba'am /
T13D4311-2:145b-47: khu ba'i mdog gzhan du 'gyur bar byed do //
T13D4311-2:145b-48: de dang 'dra bar bud med kyi mngal du khu
T13D4311-2:145b-49: ba gnas pa yang de dang 'dra bar 'gyur ro
T13D4311-2:145b-50: // rtsa la rlung nad zhugs na rtsa sbo ba dang /
T13D4311-2:145b-52: chu ba la rlung zhugs na dpyi nas brlar zur cing na ba dang /
T13D4311-2:146a-2: nga rgan gyi nad du 'gyur ro //
T13D4311-2:146a-3: rus pa'i tshigs su rlung nad zhugs na /
T13D4311-2:146a-4: myangs pa na rkyal pa rlung gis gang ba bzhin du skrang /
T13D4311-2:146a-6: lus thams cad la rlung nad zhugs na zug cing na la chag pa snyam byed /
T13D4311-2:146a-7: rengs shing rkang lag phyir g-yab par 'dod /
T13D4311-2:146a-12: nam tshong chen po'i nang kun du rlung nad yang
T13D4311-2:146a-13: dang yang zhugs te 'gro ba na lus 'gul zhing
T13D4311-2:146a-15: de la ming ni lus la nad 'jug pa zhes bya'o //
T13D4311-2:146a-16: ro smad man chad du rlung nad 'gags pa dang /
T13D4311-2:146a-17: gyen du song na snying la gnas te /
T13D4311-2:146a-18: sbu gur zhugs nas snying dang /
T13D4311-2:146a-21: de bzhin du lus thams cad gzhu ltar gug ste /
T13D4311-2:146a-23: dbugs dang rngam pa mi bde bar 'thon /
T13D4311-2:146a-24: har mig tu lta zhing 'byed 'dzums mi shes /
T13D4311-2:146a-27: de'i ming ni gzhan dbang can zhes bya'o //
T13D4311-2:146a-28: slob dpon gzhan dag na re /
T13D4311-2:146a-29: nad de'i ming aa ba da na ka zhes bya'o zhe'o //
T13D4311-2:146a-30: gal te rlung nad gzhan dbang can de snying gi gnas dang /
T13D4311-2:146a-31: re zhig bral ba lta na ni /
T13D4311-2:146a-32: skad cig nad med cing bde la /
T13D4311-2:146a-33: rlung de slar snying la zhugs na /
T13D4311-2:146a-34: yang nad snga ma ldang bar 'gyur ro //
T13D4311-2:146a-35: bud med bu byung ba'i 'og tu khrag shas cher
T13D4311-2:146a-36: 'byung ba'i rjes la rlung nad gzhan dbang gi nad
T13D4311-2:146a-37: byung ba'am / yang na snad pa'i dbang gis rlung nad byung na ni gso dka' ba yin no //
T13D4311-2:146a-38: mgrin pa'i g-yas g-yon gyi 'phar rtsa gnyis kyi nang
T13D4311-2:146a-39: du rlung zhugs na ni nam tshong yan chad gug
T13D4311-2:146a-40: cing rtsa rengs te g-yo bar gyur pa dang /
T13D4311-2:146a-41: de bzhin du rtsa chen po gzhan rnams su zhugs

T13D4311-2:146a-43: thams cad kyang gzhu ltar 'khums par 'gyur ro //
T13D4311-2:146a-44: rlung nad de'i shugs drag tu skye na ni /

T13D4311-2:146a-46: har mig tu lta zhing 'byed 'dzums mi shes /
T13D4311-2:146a-48: so 'khrig / stod du skyug / rtsib logs gnyis su zug cing na /
T13D4311-2:146b-2: rgyab kyi sgal tshigs dang mgo bo rnams rengs shing bsgul dka' ba yin te /
T13D4311-2:146b-3: rlung de'i ming ni da rgan lus nang du gug pa zhes bya'o //
T13D4311-2:146b-4: de la da rgan phyir dgye ba'i rlung gi mtshan ma yang de 'dra ste /
T13D4311-2:146b-5: khyad par du lus phyir gyed cing rlung gis mgo rgyab tu 'dren la /
T13D4311-2:146b-7: gnya' ba sos 'brad pa snyam sems /
T13D4311-2:146b-10: yan lag thams cad lhod par gyur pa de ni /
T13D4311-2:146b-11: de rgan gyi nad lus phyir dgye ba zhes bya'o //
T13D4311-2:146b-12: slob dpon kha cig na re rlung de'i ming ni gzhu ltar rengs pa zhes bya'o zhe'o //
T13D4311-2:146b-13: yang slob dpon kha cig na re de'i ming ni
T13D4311-2:146b-14: rlung nad shugs drag po zhes bya'o zhes zer ro
T13D4311-2:146b-15: // gnad kyi steng du rma 'byung ste der rlung
T13D4311-2:146b-16: la sogs pa'i nad gzhi gzhan dag rlung gis phul
T13D4311-2:146b-17: // te / rkang pa yan chad mgo bo man
T13D4311-2:146b-18: chad lus kun nad kyis khyab par byas te de
T13D4311-2:146b-20: lus skya bo rbab rbab por gyur pa ni rma'i da rgan zhes bya ste spang bar bya'o //
T13D4311-2:146b-21: gong du bshad pa'i rlung nad lnga po de dag
T13D4311-2:146b-22: thams cad kyang rlung gi shugs dang bral na ni
T13D4311-2:146b-23: nad med cing bde bar 'gyur ro //

T13D4311-2:146b-27: 'gram pa g-yas g-yon gnyis kyi rtsa ba nas bskyod cing nyams par byas te /
T13D4311-2:146b-28: kha rtag tu gdangs pa 'am yang na 'dzums par byed de /
T13D4311-2:146b-30: smra ba thams cad kyang shin tu dka' ba de
T13D4311-2:146b-31: ni 'gram pa rang gi gnas nas nyams pa zhes
T13D4311-2:146b-32: bya ba'i rlung nad ces bya'o //
T13D4311-2:146b-33: lce'i rtse mo na smra bar byed pa'i rtsa yod de /
T13D4311-2:146b-34: de'i nang du rlung zhugs nas /

T13D4311-2:146b-36: smra yang mi nus pa de ni lce ldibs pa zhes bya ba'i rlung nad ces bya'o //

T13D4311-2:146b-40: tshig drag tu smra ba dang /
T13D4311-2:147a-2: gdong yon por gcus nas sbrid pa gtong ba dang /
T13D4311-2:147a-3: gzhu sra ste ma 'dren pa dang /

T13D4311-2:147a-7: ro stod du zhugs nas kha gdong gi gzhogs phyed yon por byas te /
T13D4311-2:147a-10: lta ba rnams kyang yo bar byed do //
T13D4311-2:147a-11: des na nad pa'i mgo bo yang 'gul zhing dam par byed do //
T13D4311-2:147a-12: de bzhin du skad mi phyin pa dang /
T13D4311-2:147a-13: har mig tu lta zhing 'byed 'dzums mi shes pa dang /

T13D4311-2:147a-21: gnyid kyi nang du sdangs pa dang /

T13D4311-2:147a-25: slob dpon kha cig na re lus kyi ro smad
T13D4311-2:147a-26: kyi gzhogs phyed kyang de ltar na ba yod ces

T13D4311-2:147a-35: rlung gis lus kyi gzhogs phyed bzung ste des rtsa dang rgyus pa bskam par byas nas /

T13D4311-2:147a-38: gzhogs phyed kyi las la sbyor mi nus /

T13D4311-2:147a-41: yan lag phyogs gcig gi nad ces bya'o zhes zer ro //

T13D4311-2:148a-30: bad kan dang rlung 'khrugs pa yin te /
T13D4311-2:148a-31: de ni rkang pa brtse ba'i rlung nad ces bya'o //

T13D4311-2:148b-21: khyad par du rta la sogs pa la zhon pa'i

T13D4311-2:409b-45: la grib skams su byas nas btags pa'i phye ma'i
T13D4311-2:409b-46: zhun mar dang sbrang rtsi 'am 'o ma 'am chu
T13D4311-2:409b-47: gang yang rung ba las lde gu byas nas bldags

T13D4311-2:409b-56: gcin dang lhan cig sbyar nas 'thungs na mdze 'joms par byed do //

T13D4311-2:410a-10: nyi shu rtsa gcig lon pa dang /

T13D4311-2:410a-28: gcin srib yang srin bu'i nad dang /
T13D4311-2:410a-31: tshil nad rnams sel bar byed do //
T13D4311-2:410a-32: go bye'i 'bras bu skyon med pa brdungs te zhib

T13D4311-2:410a-34: bzhag ste / de'i khar bum pa zhabs su bu ga phug pa zhig bzhag ste /
T13D4311-2:410a-35: bum pa steng ma'i nang du ba la ta ka'i
T13D4311-2:410a-36: phye ma bcug la sa nag po'i 'jim pas kha
T13D4311-2:410a-37: dang mtshams thams cad bskus te /

T13D4311-2:410a-41: de blangs nas de'i brgyad 'gyur gyi sbrang rtsi dang /
T13D4311-2:410a-42: nyis 'gyur gyi mar dang sbyar ba'i lde gu 'di yang sbyor bar bya'o //
T13D4311-2:410a-43: cho ga gong ma bzhin du kha zas la sogs pa bsten na phan yon gong ma dang 'dra'o //
T13D4311-2:410a-44: go bye'i 'bras bu smin cing rgyas pa rang lhung
T13D4311-2:410a-45: ba srang brgya nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi bar tshad
T13D4311-2:410a-46: tsam so phag phye mar byas pa zhib mo bor
T13D4311-2:410b-1: de nas go bye rlung la skams te cham chom brdungs la /

T13D4311-2:410b-9: 'bru'i phung po'i nang du zhag bdun gyi bar du sbangs la /

T13D4311-2:410b-11: skyes bu gang gis nang re de las ran bar bsten cing bza' ste /

T13D4311-2:410b-18: snying stobs dang ldan pa dang /

T13D4311-2:410b-21: chu srang lnga brgya rtsa bcu gnyis dang /

T13D4311-2:410b-31: 'di rnams kyi phye ma btab ste /

T13D4311-2:410b-46: lus skye bar byed pa dang /
T13D4311-2:410b-47: yid gzhungs par byed pa dang /
T13D4311-2:410b-48: tshe ring bar byed pa'i mchog yin no //

T13D4311-2:411a-0: sbyor ba 'dis mi sel ba gcig kyang med de lhag par pho ba'i me drod @411a * //

T13D4311-2:411a-8: til mar gyis lus bsku ba dang /

T13D4311-2:411a-11: phyi rol gyi ngogs na skye ste /

T13D4311-2:411a-15: lo ma rgya mtsho'i nang du lhung ba dang /

T13D4311-2:411a-25: dugs byas la lus kyi dri ma dag par byas te /

T13D4311-2:411a-28: gang tsam blud la sbyin khar sngags 'di bgrang bar
T13D4311-2:411a-29: bya'o // man dz'a sa ma ra ma h'a b'i hya ;

T13D4311-2:411a-35: 'thungs pa'i 'og tu dgongs ka snum dang tshva med

T13D4311-2:411b-49: de ltar lo gcig gi bar du kha zas dang /

T13D4311-2:412a-38: na mdze nad kyis lus kyi rkang lag dang sna
